| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2650 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f8a293c0-bc7c-5f4c-a608-f2cd8dd56de9"
